T02TD3668E:281a-1: a'arya t'a r'a sto tra da sha dv'i g'a th'a /
T02TD3668E:281a-3: 'phags ma sgrom ma la bstod pa tshigs su bcad pa bcu gnyis pa /
T02TD3668E:281a-4: rje btsun ma 'phags ma sgrol ma la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02TD3668E:281a-5: bzlog dka'i srid pa'i mun pa ni //
T02TD3668E:281a-7: thugs rjes brlan pa'i thugs mnga' ba'i //
T02TD3668E:281a-8: sgrol ma la ni rtag tu 'dud //
T02TD3668E:281a-9: shin tu rmongs pa'i sems can gyis //
T02TD3668E:281a-10: glang po che rnams gsod byed ma //
T02TD3668E:281a-11: lha mo seng ge khros pa yang //
T02TD3668E:281a-13: mche ba'i mdung rtse rtse mo yis //
T02TD3668E:281a-15: khyod kyi sngags kyis bzlas pa las //
T02TD3668E:281a-17: phyogs dang nam mkha' ma lus pa'i //
T02TD3668E:281a-18: du bas khyab cing bzod par dka' //
T02TD3668E:281a-19: 'bar ba yis ni khro tshig pa //
T02TD3668E:281b-0: khyod bstod char pa me zhir @281b 'gyur ;
T02TD3668E:281b-1: / ma rungs gdengs ka las byung ba'i //
T02TD3668E:281b-2: phut sgra sgrogs shing dug mig can //
T02TD3668E:281b-3: sbrul ni lha mo khyod bstod pas /
T02TD3668E:281b-4: nam mkha' lding ni bzhin du 'joms //
T02TD3668E:281b-5: ral gris gcod pa'i 'gro ba rnams //
T02TD3668E:281b-6: khrag gis yan lag bskus pa ste //
T02TD3668E:281b-7: khyod kyi ming tsam dran pa yis //
T02TD3668E:281b-8: chom rkun nus pa med par 'gyur //
T02TD3668E:281b-9: rgyal po khros pa'i bran rnams kyis //
T02TD3668E:281b-10: skra nas bzung nas zhags pa bcings //
T02TD3668E:281b-11: btson ra spangs nas lha mo kye //
T02TD3668E:281b-13: dba' rlabs tshogs ni nam mkha' dang //
T02TD3668E:281b-14: phyogs bcur yang ni khyab byed pa //
T02TD3668E:281b-15: gru log na yang rgya mtsho las //
T02TD3668E:281b-16: khyod kyis 'phangs nas pha rol phyin / khrag dang glad pa'i 'dam gyis byugs //
T02TD3668E:281b-17: de dag bza' ba la chags pa //
T02TD3668E:281b-18: lha mo khyod kyi sngags bzlas pa //
T02TD3668E:281b-20: yan lag chad cing dri ngan pa'i //
T02TD3668E:281b-21: khrag dang zhag ni sna la 'dzag /
T02TD3668E:281b-22: khyod ni dran pa tsam gyis ni //
T02TD3668E:281b-24: bkres skom gyis gdungs gcer bu dang //
T02TD3668E:281b-25: slong ba'i yi dgas 'gro ba la //
T02TD3668E:281b-26: khyod la 'dud pa tsam gyis ni //
T02TD3668E:281b-29: de ltar dad pas khyod bstod pas //
T02TD3668E:281b-30: dge ba gang bsags de yis ni //
T02TD3668E:281b-31: 'jig rten bde ba can thob shog / rje btsun ma 'phags ma sgrol ma la bstod pa slob dpon tsantra go mis mdzad pa //
T02TD3668E:281b-32: tshigs su bcad ba bcu gnyis pa rdzogs so//
